value: Breeds ne China (Liaoning to Hubei); winters in Philippines
Manchuria and possibly northern Hopeh (Ch'in-huang-tao). Known mostly from migrants collected in Hopeh, Shaweishan (= She Shan) Island, Fukien, and Luzon (one record).
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: millet fields on migration, winters in reedbeds & grasslands

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip
